{"tid":1869921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★一名確診肺炎患者曾在 海底撈火鍋店用餐，同桌2人已被確診受感染","createTime":"2020-02-08T12:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T12:51:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"01049a518c648f3f2799c1c286e257f5c698b729","tid":1869921,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情擴散，江蘇常州市政府利用大數據手段，發現當地一名確診新冠肺炎患者，曾在海底撈火鍋店用餐，其中同桌吃飯的4男1女中，有2人已被確診受感染，其餘3人正接受醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，常州市日前發布《關於緊急擴散尋找相關接觸者的通知》，指排查確診的新冠肺炎的病例時，會進一步運用大數據。通知出又列出一宗由大數據檢出的病例，一名確診患者在上月22日與多位朋友在新北區豐臣國際的海底撈火鍋店用餐，並要求當日在該店用餐的顧客主動申報，做好防護措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200208/bkn-20200208202550354-0208_00952_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200208%2Fbkn-20200208202550354-0208_00952_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=287f6bca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200208/bkn-20200208202550354-0208_00952_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde</a>"},{"pid":"c6a2d67ea666af00423a41d516c11b1494500aa4","tid":1869921,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b79365c60c85d3826add4b5f0cf93abfdf21f9","tid":1869921,"uid":44358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:41:59.000Z","ms